{"tid":1408311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機管局網站顯示有67班離港航班及至少53班抵港取消","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:00:48.000Z","uid":288981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5c209692c3b3b6460c2003322814bb7492ba6f","tid":1408311,"uid":288981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"2019-08-05 HKT 00:48<br />\n<br />\n機管局網站顯示，今日至少有67班離港航班、以及至少53班抵港航班取消。<br />\n<br />\n機管局表示，今日可能出現一些或影響機場運作的情況，呼籲旅客聯絡航空公司，確認航班後，才出發前往機場。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發起今日「三罷」，即是罷工、罷市及罷課，要求政府回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席吳敏兒說，據她了解，有來自5間航空公司的部分員工，決定參與罷工，可能導致航班延誤或取消。她說，香港已進入決定性時刻，希望大家團結及體諒，並促請政府回應市民訴求，否則行動可能繼續升級。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472570-20190805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472570-20190805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=59623904\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472570-20190805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=018e277c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472570-20190805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}